attributes.description: Agentcore identity dashboard showcasing authentication performance and token management operations.

params.markdown:
# Identity

This dashboard provides insights into the following:
- Identity token fetch operations, including workload access tokens, resource tokens (OAuth), and Application Programming Interface (API) key retrieval metrics
- Authentication success and failure monitoring with real-time tracking of token fetch operations across different providers
- Throttling and performance analysis showing capacity constraints and operational bottlenecks for identity services
- Provider-specific breakdowns displaying top workload identities and authentication providers
